  m_Name: Intro_Level6
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  lines:
  - "Level 6: 'The Last Good Idea.'"
  - "Everything you've learned is about to be reintroduced as a slightly worse version of itself."
  - "Notice the silence? That's the soundtrack of 'almost done.'"
  - "Go on. Be heroic. Or at least be horizontal with conviction."
  - "Psst: rumors say there\'s an unlisted room if you climb higher than is reasonable."
